[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":672},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fai\u002F20250522\u002F3579637231\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fai\u002F20250522\u002F3579637231\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fai\u002F20250522\u002F3579637231\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fai\u002F20250522\u002F3579637231\u002F":648,"related:\u002Fai\u002F20250522\u002F3579637231\u002F":657},"\u002Fen\u002Fai\u002F2025\u002F05\u002F22\u002Fgithub-copilot-mcp-server-vscode-setup\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":630,"date":631,"description":25,"extension":632,"lang":633,"meta":634,"navigation":635,"path":636,"readingMinutes":637,"seo":638,"standalone":639,"stem":640,"tags":641,"tldr":645,"updated":631,"url":646,"__hash__":647},"content\u002Fai\u002FGitHub-Copilot-MCP-Server-串接-VSCode-打造-AI-開發流程教學.md","GitHub Copilot + MCP Server 串接 VSCode 打造 AI 開發流程教學","3579637231",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":622},"minimark",[11,19,23,26,30,33,36,39,42,45,48,51,85,88,92,95,111,114,120,133,138,141,146,149,191,194,197,203,206,444,447,451,454,463,466,477,483,486,489,494,503,507,514,525,528,534,537,543,546,552,556,559,565,568,571,577,580,592,595,598,604,607,612,615,618],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":17,"src":18},"GitHub Copilot + MCP Server","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002FChatGPT%20Image%202025%E5%B9%B45%E6%9C%8822%E6%97%A5%20%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8810_50_58.png",[20,21,22],"h2",{"id":22},"前言",[12,24,25],{},"近代來講，AI 開發已經成為工程師必備的技能之一，但是我們在使用 AI 工具時，總是會遇到一些狀況，如：AI 回傳的內容不如預期，或是 AI 無法理解我們的需求，這些問題都會影響我們的開發效率，所以為了解決這個問題，MCP Server 應運而生。",[20,27,29],{"id":28},"什麼是-mcp-server","什麼是 MCP Server",[12,31,32],{},"簡單來講 MCP（Model Context Protocol） 是一種 AI 協議，概念就跟 HTTP 協議一樣，只要大家都遵守這個協議，那麼就可以互相串接\u002F溝通...",[12,34,35],{},"如果要解釋這一大串的話，我覺得實在很難懂，所以我想簡單一點解釋：",[12,37,38],{},"「大家講好一個遊戲規則，然後大家都遵守這個遊戲規則，就可以一起玩這個遊戲。」",[12,40,41],{},"為什麼這樣講呢？每個服務商都有自己的規則，像是 GitHub、Figma、Google 等等，這些服務都有自己的 API，而這些 API 都有服務商自己的遊戲規則，但 AI 不可能都懂這些規則，所以我們透過一個顧問來幫我們處理這些事情，這個中介人就是 MCP Server。",[12,43,44],{},"以 GitHub 為例，當我們透過 GitHub Copilot 來發起一個請求時，GitHub Copilot 會先分析、拆解這個請求，當分析出你這個請求內容跟 GitHub 有關時，就會跑去跟 MCP Server 説：「ㄟㄟ，我這邊有一個請求是跟 GitHub 有關的，你可以幫我跟 GitHub 詢問一下這些東西在哪嗎？」，然後 MCP Server 就會去翻他的手冊（API 文件），然後告訴 GitHub Copilot：「這個東西在這裡」，然後再依照你的需求來執行\u002F回應給你結果。",[12,46,47],{},"透過這種方式 AI 的準確度可以大幅度的增加，而且也可以讓 AI 知道你在講什麼，這樣就不會出現 AI 回傳的內容不如預期的狀況了。",[12,49,50],{},"那麼講到現在，我們也差不多要進入正題了，在正題開始之前，你必須要準備好以下的環境（並安裝好）：",[52,53,54,64,71,78],"ul",{},[55,56,57],"li",{},[58,59,63],"a",{"href":60,"rel":61},"https:\u002F\u002Fcode.visualstudio.com\u002F",[62],"nofollow","Visual Studio Code",[55,65,66],{},[58,67,70],{"href":68,"rel":69},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=GitHub.copilot",[62],"GitHub Copilot",[55,72,73],{},[58,74,77],{"href":75,"rel":76},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=GitHub.copilot-chat",[62],"GitHub Copilot Chat",[55,79,80],{},[58,81,84],{"href":82,"rel":83},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.docker.com\u002F",[62],"Docker",[12,86,87],{},"準備好以上我們才能夠往下繼續唷～",[20,89,91],{"id":90},"設定並取得-mcp-server","設定並取得 MCP Server",[12,93,94],{},"那我們該如何找到自己要的 MCP Server 呢？取得的方式有兩處：",[52,96,97,104],{},[55,98,99],{},[58,100,103],{"href":101,"rel":102},"https:\u002F\u002Fmodelcontextprotocol.io\u002Fexamples",[62],"MCP 官方 Examples 頁面",[55,105,106],{},[58,107,110],{"href":108,"rel":109},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fmodelcontextprotocol\u002Fservers",[62],"MCP 的 Server 儲存庫",[12,112,113],{},"你可以從這兩處找到你想要嘗試的 MCP Server，那麼這邊我就挑選 GitHub 的 MCP Server 作為示範",[12,115,116],{},[15,117],{"alt":118,"src":119},"GitHub MCP Server","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522101009.png",[12,121,122,123,127,128,132],{},"這邊要特別提醒一下，當你點擊進去之後，這個儲存庫會是",[124,125,126],"strong",{},"棄用","的，所以你還要再點一下 ",[58,129,130],{"href":130,"rel":131},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fgithub\u002Fgithub-mcp-server",[62]," 才能到最新版的",[12,134,135],{},[15,136],{"alt":118,"src":137},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522101333.png",[12,139,140],{},"那麼接下來該怎麼做呢？你可能會找不到任何 Docker 跟安裝指令，因為 GitHub MCP Server 的安裝方式是透過這兩個標籤來進行安裝的：",[12,142,143],{},[15,144],{"alt":145,"src":119},"標籤",[12,147,148],{},"其實這兩個標籤都有幫各位寫好相關安裝連結",[150,151,156],"pre",{"className":152,"code":153,"language":154,"meta":155,"style":155},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","https:\u002F\u002Finsiders.vscode.dev\u002Fredirect\u002Fmcp\u002Finstall?name=github&inputs=%5B%7B%22id%22%3A%22github_token%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22promptString%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22GitHub%20Personal%20Access%20Token%22%2C%22password%22%3Atrue%7D%5D&config=%7B%22command%22%3A%22docker%22%2C%22args%22%3A%5B%22run%22%2C%22-i%22%2C%22--rm%22%2C%22-e%22%2C%22GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN%22%2C%22ghcr.io%2Fgithub%2Fgithub-mcp-server%22%5D%2C%22env%22%3A%7B%22GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN%22%3A%22%24%7Binput%3Agithub_token%7D%22%7D%7D\n","bash","",[157,158,159],"code",{"__ignoreMap":155},[160,161,164,168,172,176,180,183,186,188],"span",{"class":162,"line":163},"line",1,[160,165,167],{"class":166},"s_sBn","https:\u002F\u002Finsiders.vscode.dev\u002Fredirect\u002Fmcp\u002Finstall?name",[160,169,171],{"class":170},"sTRMh","=github",[160,173,175],{"class":174},"sMAXC","&inputs",[160,177,179],{"class":178},"sWyjQ","=",[160,181,182],{"class":170},"%5B%7B%22id%22%3A%22github_token%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22promptString%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22GitHub%20Personal%20Access%20Token%22%2C%22password%22%3Atrue%7D%5D",[160,184,185],{"class":174},"&config",[160,187,179],{"class":178},[160,189,190],{"class":170},"%7B%22command%22%3A%22docker%22%2C%22args%22%3A%5B%22run%22%2C%22-i%22%2C%22--rm%22%2C%22-e%22%2C%22GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN%22%2C%22ghcr.io%2Fgithub%2Fgithub-mcp-server%22%5D%2C%22env%22%3A%7B%22GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN%22%3A%22%24%7Binput%3Agithub_token%7D%22%7D%7D\n",[12,192,193],{},"這邊我示範的是 VSCode 正式版，因為 Insiders 屬於測試版本，建議一般使用者避免使用。",[12,195,196],{},"當你點下去之後，會跳出一個視窗，請選擇「安裝伺服器」",[12,198,199],{},[15,200],{"alt":201,"src":202},"安裝伺服器","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522102004.png",[12,204,205],{},"接著你的 VSCode 就會跳出 setting.json 的畫面，內容如下：",[150,207,211],{"className":208,"code":209,"language":210,"meta":155,"style":155},"language-json shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","{\n\"mcp\": {\n        \"servers\": {\n            \"github\": {\n                \"command\": \"docker\",\n                \"args\": [\n                    \"run\",\n                    \"-i\",\n                    \"--rm\",\n                    \"-e\",\n                    \"GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN\",\n                    \"ghcr.io\u002Fgithub\u002Fgithub-mcp-server\"\n                ],\n                \"env\": {\n                    \"GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN\": \"${input:github_token}\"\n                }\n            }\n        },\n        \"inputs\": [\n            {\n                \"id\": \"github_token\",\n                \"type\": \"promptString\",\n                \"description\": \"GitHub Personal Access Token\",\n                \"password\": true\n            }\n        ]\n    }\n}\n","json",[157,212,213,218,228,236,244,259,268,276,284,292,300,308,314,320,328,338,344,350,356,364,370,383,396,409,421,426,432,438],{"__ignoreMap":155},[160,214,215],{"class":162,"line":163},[160,216,217],{"class":174},"{\n",[160,219,221,225],{"class":162,"line":220},2,[160,222,224],{"class":223},"sKpQp","\"mcp\"",[160,226,227],{"class":174},": {\n",[160,229,231,234],{"class":162,"line":230},3,[160,232,233],{"class":223},"        \"servers\"",[160,235,227],{"class":174},[160,237,239,242],{"class":162,"line":238},4,[160,240,241],{"class":223},"            \"github\"",[160,243,227],{"class":174},[160,245,247,250,253,256],{"class":162,"line":246},5,[160,248,249],{"class":223},"                \"command\"",[160,251,252],{"class":174},": ",[160,254,255],{"class":170},"\"docker\"",[160,257,258],{"class":174},",\n",[160,260,262,265],{"class":162,"line":261},6,[160,263,264],{"class":223},"                \"args\"",[160,266,267],{"class":174},": [\n",[160,269,271,274],{"class":162,"line":270},7,[160,272,273],{"class":170},"                    \"run\"",[160,275,258],{"class":174},[160,277,279,282],{"class":162,"line":278},8,[160,280,281],{"class":170},"                    \"-i\"",[160,283,258],{"class":174},[160,285,287,290],{"class":162,"line":286},9,[160,288,289],{"class":170},"                    \"--rm\"",[160,291,258],{"class":174},[160,293,295,298],{"class":162,"line":294},10,[160,296,297],{"class":170},"                    \"-e\"",[160,299,258],{"class":174},[160,301,303,306],{"class":162,"line":302},11,[160,304,305],{"class":170},"                    \"GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN\"",[160,307,258],{"class":174},[160,309,311],{"class":162,"line":310},12,[160,312,313],{"class":170},"                    \"ghcr.io\u002Fgithub\u002Fgithub-mcp-server\"\n",[160,315,317],{"class":162,"line":316},13,[160,318,319],{"class":174},"                ],\n",[160,321,323,326],{"class":162,"line":322},14,[160,324,325],{"class":223},"                \"env\"",[160,327,227],{"class":174},[160,329,331,333,335],{"class":162,"line":330},15,[160,332,305],{"class":223},[160,334,252],{"class":174},[160,336,337],{"class":170},"\"${input:github_token}\"\n",[160,339,341],{"class":162,"line":340},16,[160,342,343],{"class":174},"                }\n",[160,345,347],{"class":162,"line":346},17,[160,348,349],{"class":174},"            }\n",[160,351,353],{"class":162,"line":352},18,[160,354,355],{"class":174},"        },\n",[160,357,359,362],{"class":162,"line":358},19,[160,360,361],{"class":223},"        \"inputs\"",[160,363,267],{"class":174},[160,365,367],{"class":162,"line":366},20,[160,368,369],{"class":174},"            {\n",[160,371,373,376,378,381],{"class":162,"line":372},21,[160,374,375],{"class":223},"                \"id\"",[160,377,252],{"class":174},[160,379,380],{"class":170},"\"github_token\"",[160,382,258],{"class":174},[160,384,386,389,391,394],{"class":162,"line":385},22,[160,387,388],{"class":223},"                \"type\"",[160,390,252],{"class":174},[160,392,393],{"class":170},"\"promptString\"",[160,395,258],{"class":174},[160,397,399,402,404,407],{"class":162,"line":398},23,[160,400,401],{"class":223},"                \"description\"",[160,403,252],{"class":174},[160,405,406],{"class":170},"\"GitHub Personal Access Token\"",[160,408,258],{"class":174},[160,410,412,415,417],{"class":162,"line":411},24,[160,413,414],{"class":223},"                \"password\"",[160,416,252],{"class":174},[160,418,420],{"class":419},"sCcAr","true\n",[160,422,424],{"class":162,"line":423},25,[160,425,349],{"class":174},[160,427,429],{"class":162,"line":428},26,[160,430,431],{"class":174},"        ]\n",[160,433,435],{"class":162,"line":434},27,[160,436,437],{"class":174},"    }\n",[160,439,441],{"class":162,"line":440},28,[160,442,443],{"class":174},"}\n",[12,445,446],{},"到這邊為止，我們已經把 VSCode 的 MCP Server 設定完成了，接著我們要來取得 GitHub 的 Personal Access Token，這邊的 Token 需要有 repo 權限，這樣才能夠讓 MCP Server 正常運作。",[20,448,450],{"id":449},"取得-github-personal-access-token","取得 GitHub Personal Access Token",[12,452,453],{},"取得方式很簡單，請你透過下方連結進入 GitHub 的設定頁面：",[52,455,456],{},[55,457,458],{},[58,459,462],{"href":460,"rel":461},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fsettings\u002Fpersonal-access-tokens\u002Fnew",[62],"GitHub Personal Access Token",[12,464,465],{},"欄位這邊我直接提供參考：",[52,467,468,471,474],{},[55,469,470],{},"Token name：GitHub MCP Server",[55,472,473],{},"Expiration：No expiration",[55,475,476],{},"Repository access：All repositories",[12,478,479],{},[15,480],{"alt":481,"src":482},"取得 Token","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522102440.png",[12,484,485],{},"其他你可以依照你的需求來調整，例如只給予特定的 repository 存取權限等等。",[12,487,488],{},"那麼點下「Generate token」之後，你就會取得一組 Token，請將這組 Token 複製起來，稍後我們會使用到",[12,490,491],{},[15,492],{"alt":481,"src":493},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522102610.png",[495,496,497],"blockquote",{},[12,498,499,502],{},[124,500,501],{},"Note","\n請勿將這組 Token 洩漏給任何人。",[20,504,506],{"id":505},"設定-vscode-的-github-personal-access-token","設定 VSCode 的 GitHub Personal Access Token",[12,508,509,510,513],{},"接著該怎麼輸入呢？請你按下 ",[157,511,512],{},"F1"," 叫出 VSCode 的指令面板，接著輸入：",[150,515,519],{"className":516,"code":517,"language":518,"meta":155,"style":155},"language-txt shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast",">MCP:List Servers\n","txt",[157,520,521],{"__ignoreMap":155},[160,522,523],{"class":162,"line":163},[160,524,517],{},[12,526,527],{},"你應該會看到一個「MCP：列出伺服器」，選擇它後，接著選擇「github」",[12,529,530],{},[15,531],{"alt":532,"src":533},"選擇 github","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522103022.png",[12,535,536],{},"接著選擇「啟動伺服器」，這時候應該會跳出一個視窗要求你輸入 GitHub Personal Access Token，請將剛剛取得的 Token 貼上去，然後按下 Enter 鍵即可。",[12,538,539],{},[15,540],{"alt":541,"src":542},"輸入 Token","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522103106.png",[12,544,545],{},"接著你就會看到 VSCode 開始啟動 MCP Server，並安裝 Docker，只要你看到這個畫面就代表 MCP Server 啟動成功了",[12,547,548],{},[15,549],{"alt":550,"src":551},"啟動成功","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522103141.png",[20,553,555],{"id":554},"測試-mcp-server","測試 MCP Server",[12,557,558],{},"接下來就要來測試 MCP Server 是否正常運作了，請你打開 GitHub Copilot Chat，然後切換到 Agent 模式",[12,560,561],{},[15,562],{"alt":563,"src":564},"Agent 模式","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522103719.png",[12,566,567],{},"接著就可以開始問它關於 GitHub 相關的問題了！例如...我的 GitHub 帳號底下有多少儲存庫？",[12,569,570],{},"只要你有看到畫面有寫「MCP 伺服器」，就代表這一次的請求詢問有經過 MCP Server，然後再回傳給你結果",[12,572,573],{},[15,574],{"alt":575,"src":576},"詢問問題","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522104000.png",[12,578,579],{},"那們我該如何知道這個 MCP 有支援哪些功能呢？有三種方式：",[52,581,582,589],{},[55,583,584],{},[58,585,588],{"href":586,"rel":587},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fgithub\u002Fgithub-mcp-server?tab=readme-ov-file#tools",[62],"官方 MCP Server Tools 區塊",[55,590,591],{},"MCP Server Source Code",[12,593,594],{},"這邊我是推薦看「官方 MCP Server Tools 區塊」會比較快。",[12,596,597],{},"另一種更快速的方式是透過 GitHub Copilot Chat Tools",[12,599,600],{},[15,601],{"alt":602,"src":603},"GitHub Copilot Chat Tools","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522104418.png",[12,605,606],{},"點擊之後，將會跳出這個 GitHub Copilot Chat 的工具列表，這邊會列出所有支援的工具",[12,608,609],{},[15,610],{"alt":602,"src":611},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fmcp-github-copilot\u002F20250522104513.png",[12,613,614],{},"那麼以上就是完整的 GitHub Copilot + MCP Server 串接 VSCode 的教學哩～",[12,616,617],{},"像是透過 MCP Server 你可以更準確的要求 AI 去做某些事情，像是自然語言來建立儲存庫等等",[619,620,621],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}",{"title":155,"searchDepth":220,"depth